snippet.title: NOBUNAGA'S AMBITION: Awakening Complete Edition: Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit the website: https://www.koeitecmoamerica.com/nobunaga/awakening/ce/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=AnnounceUS&utm_id=Caption

Conquer Warring States Japan under one banner.

NOBUNAGA'S AMBITION: Awakening Complete Edition is coming June 5, 2025 to Nintendo Switch™ 2 and PlayStation®5! 

This edition includes the base game and additional content,and includes additional content such as new scenarios and other elements.

Join the #KTFamily:
X: https://twitter.com/KoeiTecmoUS
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/koeitecmous
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/koeitecmous/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/KTFamily

*Screens are taken from an in-development version.

#NAAwakening #NintendoSwitch2
